basics.name: Jonathan Fox
basics.label: Programmer
basics.description:
An innovative Front End developer with experience building and maintaining professional websites. Proficient in JavaScript, React, and CSS. Comfortable with modern libraries and frameworks. Passionate about bringing value to users through
practical, accessible web apps.

work.summary:
Unspoke.io is a supply management platform that helps
business owners manage their businesses efficiently by
providing data visibility and management tools.
highlights: Maintain website by developing new components using JavaScript, React, Material-UI, and Feathers.js

Collaborate with members from other teams, including
UX designers, management, and back end engineers

Research new technologies to identify ways to increase
efficiency and add functionality to the platform

work.summary: JITS is an app that provides services to small businesses by connecting them with freelance workers.
highlights: Led production of the Android JITS app with Android Studio
Collaborated with back end engineers to access server API

projects.name: HSLookup.net
projects.summary: HSLookup.net improves Hearthstone players' understanding of the game by giving them valuable statistics and probability data.
highlights: Used React to create a web app that gives users access to filter options and displays card data.
Created a server on Heroku that enables the client to use up-to-date card data from the official Blizzard API
Styled the site with CSS to work well on desktop and mobile
